Class ClientMain

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.ClientMain
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Constants

    public class ClientMain
extends java.lang.Object
implements Constants
    Client main initializes a connection with the server through sockets and constructs the input and output streams for strings and objects. Also handles the login client server interactions.
    Author:
    Justin, Magnus, Robert
